  "html": "<div class=\"spes\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etymology_2\">Etymology</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=spes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Etymology\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p>From <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Italic_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Italic language\">Proto-Italic</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"itc-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/sp%C4%93s\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/sp&#x113;s\">*sp&#x113;s</a></i>, from <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Indo-European_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Indo-European language\">Proto-Indo-European</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"ine-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/sp%C3%A9h%E2%82%81s\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/sp&#xE9;h&#x2081;s\">*sp&#xE9;h&#x2081;s</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">prosperity</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>, from <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"ine-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/speh%E2%82%81-\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/speh&#x2081;-\">*speh&#x2081;-</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">to succeed, prosper</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">[1]</a></sup> Cognate with <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_English\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Old English\">Old English</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"ang\"><a href=\"/wiki/sped#Old_English\" title=\"sped\">sp&#x113;d</a></i>, whence <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:English language\">English</a></span> <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"en\"><a href=\"/wiki/speed#English\" title=\"speed\">speed</a></i>.\n</p><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pronunciation\">Pronunciation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=spes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Pronunciation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><ul><li><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Classical Latin\">Classical</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:Latin pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/spe&#x2D0;s/</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ecclesiastical_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ecclesiastical Latin\">Ecclesiastical</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:Latin pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/spes/</span>, <span class=\"IPA\">[sp&#x25B;s]</span></li></ul><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Noun\">Noun</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=spes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: Noun\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"la\">sp&#x113;s</strong>&#xA0;<span class=\"gender\"><abbr title=\"feminine gender\">f</abbr></span> (<i>genitive</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/spei#Latin\" title=\"spei\">spe&#x12B;</a></b>); <i><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_fifth_declension\" title=\"Appendix:Latin fifth declension\">fifth declension</a></i>\n</p><ol><li><a href=\"/wiki/hope\" title=\"hope\">hope</a> <span class=\"gloss-brac\">(</span><span class=\"gloss-content\">belief or expectation that something wished for can or will happen</span><span class=\"gloss-brac\">)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/expectation\" title=\"expectation\">expectation</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/anticipation\" title=\"anticipation\">anticipation</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/apprehension\" title=\"apprehension\">apprehension</a> <span class=\"gloss-brac\">(</span><span class=\"gloss-content\">act or state of looking forward to an event as about to happen</span><span class=\"gloss-brac\">)</span></li></ol><h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Declension\">Declension</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=spes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Declension\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4><p><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_fifth_declension\" title=\"Appendix:Latin fifth declension\">Fifth-declension</a> noun.<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r50505018\">.mw-parser-output .inflection-table-la .corner-header,.mw-parser-output .inflection-table-la .number-header,.mw-parser-output .inflection-table-la .case-header{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output .inflection-table-la .corner-header,.mw-parser-output .inflection-table-la .number-he